{"tid":1262831,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕人快點登記做選民7月2日截止啦","createTime":"2019-06-28T01:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T05:23:57.000Z","uid":265915,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ef1b9abd1f8b2d64ed7bb0b5e09dbaeae3c46f","tid":1262831,"uid":265915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"各位年輕人們，<br />\n<br />\n原來今年9月24日前過18歲生日 都可以7月2日前登記咗先 成為合資格選民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ospprdwcdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/changeLocale.do?language=zh&amp;country=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdwcdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2FchangeLocale.do%3Flanguage%3Dzh%26country%3DHK&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=78d8aaa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdwcdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/changeLocale.do?language=zh&amp;country=HK</a><br />\n<br />\n可以電子方法填寫及遞交選民登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379468/【選民登記】教你電子填寫及遞交選民登記申請表！手機＋電腦適用\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2379468%2F%E3%80%90%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E3%80%91%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E5%A1%AB%E5%AF%AB%E5%8F%8A%E9%81%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%EF%BC%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=484e50e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2379468/【選民登記】教你電子填寫及遞交選民登記申請表！手機＋電腦適用</a><br />\n<br />\n要班仆街保皇比天收 到時靠你一票(同摧毀幾張鐵票)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同意請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037a0aab45fe1674e23458362165a19cb6e7b8b3","tid":1262831,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8f34c87929aa700fa10109ea9f4c6fb4369cb5af","tid":1262831,"uid":173334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"